y treacherous dungeons, defeat enemies and bosses in order to secure items for your boss, <i>Papa Corporal Cone</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-25 dungeons to explore, each with unique themes and challenges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fight your way through a variety of dungeons full of dangerous beasts and bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Many dungeons include unique challenges you must face!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/4b5d0511ff9fec38bcae4a100666e0b8.poster.avif?t=1748036187\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/4b5d0511ff9fec38bcae4a100666e0b8.webm?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/4b5d0511ff9fec38bcae4a100666e0b8.mp4?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive weapon system!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many different weapons in Cone Flyers Mercenaries, each producing unique and exciting weapon combinations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Choose a primary and secondary weapon combo</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Choose the right tool for the job! Some weapons may not work well for some situations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Unlock new and exciting weapons as you progress through the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/b9aaf7c3171242a3397bf3a1746295dd.poster.avif?t=1748036187\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/b9aaf7c3171242a3397bf3a1746295dd.webm?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/b9aaf7c3171242a3397bf3a1746295dd.mp4?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Precision Platforming</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your reflexes and motor skills over and over again with this game's precision platforming! Your knowledge on game mechanics will be tested with the unique challenges you'll face on each planet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Use weapons to your advantage! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-No obnoxiously long respawn animations, so you'll be back to kickin in no time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Trial and error.. some of these screens will take you a really long time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/31bf216324056db27b32ae5cee62f938.poster.avif?t=1748036187\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/31bf216324056db27b32ae5cee62f938.webm?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3046120/extras/31bf216324056db27b32ae5cee62f938.mp4?t=1748036187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What are you waiting for? This game simply has everything! And remember.. The Life Engine awaits...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
